des: "This recipe is great for both yellow and chocolate flavored cakes! It makes a light, fluffy, and SERIOUSLY moist cake."
ins: Make the batter following the directions on the box, EXCEPT replace 2 teaspoons water with an equal amount of vanilla.  Fold in sour cream.  Bake according to directions given for baking a bundt cake. Cool on rack, place on serving plate, and dust with confectioners sugar.
